PROCESS

From Steps to

Pulz Points.

Step 1

Connect Wallet

Open the Pulz dApp in your browser and connect your preferred Web3 wallet (e.g., MetaMask, WalletConnect)

Step 2

Start Activity

Choose your activity type (Run, Ride, Walk, Gym) and tap Start Tracking to begin recording.

Step 3

Track in Real Time

Monitor your distance, duration, and points on the live dashboard. Pulz auto-pauses when you stop moving.

Step 4

Finish & Validate

End your session and let Pulz’s anti-cheat system verify your activity. Points are awarded based on distance, duration, and trust score

Step 5

Redeem & Enjoy

Use Pulz to join challenges, unlock rewards in the marketplace, or access premium features.

FAQ

Answers to

Your Queries

What is Pulz?

Pulz is a Web3 fitness dApp that tracks your real-world activities using your device’s GPS and motion sensors, rewarding you with Pulz Points that can be redeemed for various rewards.

Do I need to download an app?

Which activities can I track?

Is my data private?
